arch note
name notes on the dragon lords
msg
  The three dragon lords,sons of the
dragon mother,are immensly powerful.
Their greed knows no bounds,and they
wish for complete immortality.
However,they are immune to most
attacks,except their natural
weaknesses. Fire lord being weak
against cold,Ice lord being weak
against fire,and Thunder lord being
weak against fire. Their skin is so
tough,however,that physical attacks do
not hurt them at all. And they were
given complete protection from magical
attacks,by ruggilli. It is also said
that they carry weapons given to them
by ruggilli,these weapons are said to
be so powerful,that no normal being
may use them. But,fortunatly,they
carry other rewards that they achieved
by themselves. 

  The high dragon lords dwell in the
mountain of Gondoria.  
endmsg
