name notes on the balrog
msg
  The balrog who took the mines of
morgria,guards great treasure. In the
treasure is a Black Dragon Mail,making
the wearer resistant to
fire,electricity,cold,and chaos;a
Fire Star of Great Power;a Red
Crystal,able to fire evil flames;and
an Evil Shield. But,may the adventurer
be warned,the artifacts have great side
effects. Even touching them may bring
the adventurer trouble. I would stay
away from those artifacts...
endmsg
