arch c_sage
name old librarian,Bartud
msg
@match necromancer|Necromancer
 I have been doing research on
him,with books from all over Erthos
and the Elven Lands! He is over a
thousand years old,the dark spirits of
Devourers have given him immortality.
He never ages,however,that just means
that he never dies of age. He can be
killed in battle. The Devourers gave
him this power,due to his loyalty and
deeds. He is their greatest mortal
servent! To help him in his dark quest
to succumb the world to their
religion,they gave him the Dark
Behemoth. The Dark Behemoth is a
powerful beast,impervious to most
attacks. The necromancer is part of
the Black Alliance,as he believes that
this will help him in his quest. 
@match weakness|Weakness
  I have not found out the Dark
Behemoth's weakness yet. But I hear
there is a sage somewhere who knows
the behemoth's weakness. 
@match Balrog|balrog|dragon|Dragon
I have done some research on that
subject,you may look at some of my
notes.
@match hi|hello
Sorry,i'm a little busy right now. If
you don't have any thing important to
say,i must get back to my research...
endmsg
